---
title: Bean, Beef & Bacon Loaded Sweet Potato Wedges with Zesty Soured Cream and Spring Onion
description: These Bean, Beef & Bacon Loaded Sweet Potato Wedges are a crowd pleaser and one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bean-beef-bacon-loaded-sweet-potato-wedges-3cbdf4ba-fe0fcf70.jpg
